{"id":1173689,"date":[{"year":1998,"month":10,"day":25}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"画刊","special_issue":"(美术长廊)","column":"","genre":"","count":"366","ytitle":"","mtitle":"’98上海美术双年展","ftitle":"——作品选","authors":["方增先"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"由上海美术馆、梁洁华艺术基金会联合主办的’98上海(美术)双年展，以“融合与拓展”为主题，参展作品以近年来的水墨创作为中心，包括各种风格形式，充分展示了艺术家对水墨这一具有极大的兼容性和延展性的多方位探求，以及他们在艺术创作中表现的丰富想象力和才情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本届双年展倡导宽松的艺术氛围和严谨学术态度的传统，鼓励探索、繁荣创作、拓展友谊，为促进中国当代艺术发展，增进中外文化交流作出贡献。　方增先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>母与子　方增先</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>张道兴</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>赶海　张道兴</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>王孟奇</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>泡茶须用曼生壶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王孟奇</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040204.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>王赞</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>血浓于水——白求恩　王赞</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040205.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>舒传熹</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>生命之树　舒传熹</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040206.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>赵奇</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>马哟，你慢些走　赵奇</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98ap040207.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT cla